author: Brian Johnson
title: Knutson finishes $7 million Tradewinds Buffet remodel
text:
Home / Brief / Knutson finishes $7 million Tradewinds Buffet remodel Knutson finishes $7 million Tradewinds Buffet remodel By: Brian Johnson September 8, 2015 3:35 pm 0 St. Louis Park-based Knutson Construction recently completed a $7 million, 16,000-square-foot remodel of the Tradewinds Buffet for Treasure Island Resort and Casino in Welch, Minnesota. The buffet, which reopened Sept. 3, features high-end finishes that came from locations across the world, including natural stone onyx and a variety of tiles and ultramodern light fixtures from Italy, ...
